   College. Three of the most important years  
   of your life. Three years of studies (at    
   times) and sheer indulgence. Indulgence in  
   all the little pleasures that a carefree    
   life has to offer. But it isn't always about
   ragging, fuchacha parties, college fests,   
   races, and churning out ways to whack some  
   extra pocket money from your parents. It's  
   sometimes hard, ugly, and complicated. More 
   so, when you really need to get admission   
   in the coolest college in town and you know 
   you don't deserve it. And to top that, you  
   get yourself involved in the most bizarre   
   stations that could crack you into pieces   
   before you could crack it.
